description:
Swan Meat celebrates her ace 'BLOOD SUPERNOVA' EP with a suite of eardrum-belting remixes from Manuka Honey, Lobsta B, BABii, WTCHCRFT and Dr Dr4kken.

Swan Meat's fusion of gutter-strength hard dance, videogame soundtracks (think 'Castlevania'), psy trance and baroque music was perfectly realised on last year's 'BLOOD SUPERNOVA', and now she gets a lap of honor with a little help from her friends.
